Suicide rate, male (per 100,000 people)
SDG 3.4 By 2030, reduce by one third premature mortality from non-communicable diseases through prevention and treatment and promote mental health and well-being
Dimension: Human Security
Definition: Number of deaths from purposely self-inflicted injuries, expressed per 100,000 people in the reference population.
Source: WHO (World Health Organization) (2019). Global Health Observatory. www.who.int/gho/. Accessed 15 July 2019.
